text: Polyacanthia stictica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1874, originally under the genus Poecilippe.BioLib.cz - Polyacanthia stictica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1874
title: Polyacanthia stictica
